恐龍隻手都有用架喎<br />\n利申:恐龍戰隊紅戰士</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴龍係鬼鬼祟祟個隻吖，定係嘩個隻？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句好熟 唔記得邊到岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24561cd8260619b3d3876092ae6aed9983fda05f","tid":58781,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會係用來平衡？"},{"pid":"de45b04fd33437eb9255978ff74f8eb09b50fd42","tid":58781,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係咪想講暴龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多恐龍隻手都有用架喎<br />\n利申:恐龍戰隊紅戰士</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴龍係鬼鬼祟祟個隻吖，定係嘩個隻？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句好熟 唔記得邊到岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係嘩個雙<br />\n鬼鬼崇崇個隻好冇陰公嫁，專追住細蚊仔咬<br />\n唔會，中國呢條肯定唔會"},{"pid":"f4171e607fc54e8ce72a5eacf018cdeaa51125d3","tid":58781,"uid":36980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴龍係鬼鬼祟祟個隻吖，定係嘩個隻？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句好熟 唔記得邊到岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係嘩個雙<br />\n鬼鬼崇崇個隻好冇陰公嫁，專追住細蚊仔咬<br />\n唔會，中國呢條肯定唔會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啦我記返起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192efaa9ccfa126cd91dacfece9626508af7e215","tid":58781,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係用來平衡？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我既推測係用左平衡<br />\n係網上搵到一d關於暴龍前肢作用既推斷<br />\n<a href=\"http://web.fg.tp.edu.tw/~earth/course/dino90/dino21.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.fg.tp.edu.tw%2F~earth%2Fcourse%2Fdino90%2Fdino21.htm&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=36b8cac2\" target=\"_blank\">http://web.fg.tp.edu.tw/~earth/course/dino90/dino21.htm</a><br />\n可以參考一下"},{"pid":"336bfae01744b8a83db6cd351fb109d310a987c7","tid":58781,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"用波棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a40a2d4b773c378939d7e7226c1caee3f09c435","tid":58781,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:15:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://100000whys.hkep.com/pdf/select/why_select_paleontology_2.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F100000whys.hkep.com%2Fpdf%2Fselect%2Fwhy_select_paleontology_2.pdf&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=76d5e6c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://100000whys.hkep.com/pdf/select/why_select_paleontology_2.pdf</a><br />\n呢個係另一篇既文章<br />\n科學家未能確定有咩真正用途<br />\n但亦提出左幾種假設<br />\n有興趣既可以睇睇"},{"pid":"4b48d23e3e23443f75d0b9caab0eb5e372a03d58","tid":58781,"uid":41261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"點解加多個閪字會咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a2b765081694326cda4c2a6d2d61e9b52f6faa","tid":58781,"uid":1137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:43:57.000Z","msg":"㩒下個喇叭啦"},{"pid":"bd3411847edc849e98d3baf9dd0fe4b6cc635e52","tid":58781,"uid":14383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"第一個留言真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c4fb85d9353cb1ae3db619ea34d1ccd3beec2b","tid":58781,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T10:11:22.000Z","msg":"去野餐用"},{"pid":"dca3cfa6daf3e5955537956498bec209cf861